.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[C]omega\f[] : optional, float, default = 0
The angular rotation rate of the planet.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[C]r\f[] : optional, float, default = \f[C]r0\f[]
The radius of the reference sphere that the Taylor expansion of the
